<template>
    <button id="id_button_token" @click="getTokens">Solicitar Token</button>
    <input type="text" v-model="username" value="Usuario">
    <input type="text" v-model="password" value="Contrasenia">
</template>

<script>
import TokenService from '@/services/TokenService';


    export default{
        name: '',

        data(){
            return {
                username: '',
                password: ''
            }
        },
        methods:{
            getTokens(){
                TokenService.getTokens(this.username,this.password)
            }
        },

        // created(){

    }

</script>
